_sText:
I couldn't find a map for this game mode so I made one! (my first map)

CTs = snipers

Ts = runners

goal of the Ts is to avoid getting sniped and make it to the end
goal of the CTs is to snipe the Ts

map rules for gameplay:
long round time
max start money(so the CTs can buy awp, scout, etc. , you make the rules up with your colleages)
